# Sprint 5: User Favorites and Weekly Planning

## User Story 20: Star a recipe as a favorite
- Allow users to mark recipes as favorites.
- Display a visual indicator for favorited recipes.

## User Story 21: Unstar a recipe
- Allow users to remove recipes from their favorites.
- Confirm successful removal of recipes from favorites.

## User Story 22: Create weekly dinner lists
- Manage weekly dinner lists for specific weeks.
- Provide functionality to view, edit, and delete lists.

## User Story 23: Add dishes to weekly dinner lists
- Add recipes to dinner lists, organized by day and mealtime.
- Save changes to dinner lists automatically.